MeteoSwiss data
---------------
The generated Parquet sample files are derived from MeteoSwiss Open Data E4
local forecasts. MeteoSwiss Open Data is published under CC BY 4.0 according
to the MeteoSwiss terms of use.

Required meteorological data acknowledgement:
Source: MeteoSwiss

Do not imply that MeteoSwiss endorses this project or a particular use of the
data.

Derived surface data
--------------------
The optional polygon and hexagon Parquet files are visualization layers created
by this project from MeteoSwiss forecast points. They are not official
MeteoSwiss gridded products.

Those derived surfaces are clipped with a Swiss boundary file from the Federal
Spatial Data Infrastructure / swisstopo. When publishing those surfaces, use:
Source: MeteoSwiss; © Data: swisstopo

